-*-parse-options:lamgrow-makes-no-sense-*-
# Called when lamgrow is invoked with the tm module
# No parameters are passed
Invoking "lamgrow" in a batch environment such as PBS currently does
not make any sense -- LAM only has the nodes that TM has allocated,
and therefore cannot grow the LAM universe.

Aborting.
